newsitem.title: EGYPT: Egypt pound overnight, one week rates narrow.
newsitem.headline: Egypt pound overnight, one week rates narrow.

text.p: Overnight interbank rates on the Egyptian pound narrowed in a liquid private sector market on Tuesday to between 10 and 10-1/16 percent from Monday's range of 9-3/16 and 10-1/2 percent, bankers said.
They said one-week rates were between 10 and 10-1/4 against 9-1/4 and 10-3/8 percent on Monday.

State-owned banks maintained their minimum overnight lending rate at 10-1/2 percent. But bankers said they expected them to lower their rate in line with last week's discount rate which fell by 1/4 to 13-1/4 percent.
